{"name":"Zach Darnold","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Crimson Syndicate, Trusted Member","alignment":"Neutral Evil","hitDice":"15","armorName":"studded leather","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":9,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"97 (15d8 + 30)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"20","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"10","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Darno","desc":"[MON] is an \"explosive\" \"gunslinger.\" He's resistant to all damage from him and his allies' explosives."},{"name":"Fire Zone","desc":"All creatures on fire take [1d4] fire damage at the start of their turn. This fire can be put out with the help action."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two attacks with his Dynamite or Petrol Bomb."},{"name":"Dynamite","desc":"[MON] recklessly hurls a dynamite at a creature. [DEX ATK] to hit, range 30/60 ft. _Hit:_ All creatures within a 5ft. radius take [DEX 2D6] force damage."},{"name":"Petrol Bomb","desc":"[MON] hurls a volatile can of gasoline at a creature. [STR ATK] to hit, range 30/60 ft. _Hit_: [STR 2d6] bludgeoning damage. If the creature is burning, this does [4d6] fire damage and [4d6] force damage instead within a 30ft. radius. This damage is halved if any creatures within that range succeed a **DC [STR SAVE]** Dex save."},{"name":"Flaming Bottle","desc":"[MON] hurls an explosive bottle of fire up to 60ft. All creatures within a 30ft. radius take [8d6] fire damage if they fail a **DC [DEX SAVE]** Dex Save and start burning. If they succeed, they take half the damage."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"dex","order":1}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"sleight of Hand","stat":"dex"},{"name":"survival","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Zach","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}